Package: clincsmr
Title: Perform Centralized Statistical Monitoring for Clinical Trials
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Feinan", "Lu", email="fnlu@overlandpharma.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8963-5827"))
Description: A set of functions to perform centralized statistical monitoring 
    (CSM). You provide the data in format described in the help document, tell
    'clincsmr' what method to be applied, it will provide you with desired 
    tables and figures.
